Package org.dmsextension.paperless.client

Klasse PaperlessClient

java.lang.Object
org.dmsextension.paperless.client.PaperlessClient
public class PaperlessClient extends Object
Instances of this class are capable of communicating with Paperless-ngx. Certain convenience methods like uploadDocument(File) are already implemented, you can also instantiate your own IEndpoint class and call execute(IEndpoint, IDto) and configure the call yourself.
